  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"957\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=731&amp;height=450\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"450\" data-width=\"731\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232256\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a23d442c-e450-4b75-a7b3-887c0a25fd3b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=731&amp;height=450 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=731&amp;height=450 1x\"></span><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p /><p><em>PxrOcclusion</em> is a non-photorealistic integrator that can be used to render ambient occlusion, among other effects.</p><p>When rendering with physical based integrators it's important to note that occlusion is naturally part of the lighting calculation. This is an effect of indirect or &quot;ambient&quot; light being reflected away or darkened in corners, crevices, cracks, and more. However, in final images it might be desirable to add more of this affect for art direction. You can use this to &quot;knock back&quot; or &quot;deepen&quot; details in your image artificially. This pass is typically applied as an image multiplication or &quot;mult&quot; in a compositing application.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"18ec3462-a552-4318-893e-ec24d12f0394\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>Diffuse and specular ray depth have no effect for this integrator.</p></div></div><h4 id=\"PxrOcclusion-SampleDistribution\">Sample Distribution</h4><p>Different samples distributions can be used to create different occlusion effects.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_distribution0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_distribution0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_distribution0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232253\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_distribution0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d280ebc4-27df-424a-a00d-eebb7a753df3\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_distribution0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_distribution0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_distribution1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_distribution1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_distribution1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232250\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_distribution1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"2b11d0f1-c223-448b-8bbd-cb6a473c2f1c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_distribution1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_distribution1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_distribution2.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_distribution2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_distribution2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232247\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_distribution2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"86fd7b20-780b-409e-9ef8-62e8bf1f25b7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_distribution2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_distribution2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"46fef63b-6256-4ab7-a8cc-94ec861f7ffc\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p /></th><th class=\"confluenceTh\"><p><strong>Description</strong></p></th></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><strong>Uniform</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Rays are not weighted in any particular direction in the hemisphere above the shading point.</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><strong>Cosine</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Cosine distribution is a commonly used to render ambient occlusion.</p></td></tr><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p><strong>Reflection</strong></p></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><p>Generate samples based on the the reflection lobe of the assigned material. Materials with only a diffuse BRDF will have a result similar to the <strong>cosine</strong> setting above.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><h4 id=\"PxrOcclusion-CosineSpread\">Cosine Spread</h4><p>Sample spread of rays when using cosine distribution. A value of 1.0 gives a perfect Lambertian distribution.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232241\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"fb36a4d5-b3df-4fa4-bae7-2facbc74dfe2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723848&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723848&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232238\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"05213e2a-4cce-448f-ba53-989e289d8ea6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723848&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723848&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread2.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232244\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"4c6108d8-979a-48da-b763-603b627f0f4d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_cosineSpread2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330724016&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h4 id=\"PxrOcclusion-MaxDistance\">Max Distance</h4><p>As each point is shaded, rays reach into the scene to strike nearby objects. In some cases, like an interior, this may produce a dark or black result. You can reduce that distance using this control. Note this is measured in scene units. The default is 0 or infinite.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_maxDistance0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_maxDistance0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_maxDistance0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232229\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_maxDistance0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6aab3aa3-bdee-42c4-82c7-0225116fc908\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_maxDistance0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_maxDistance0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_maxDistance1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_maxDistance1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723848&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_maxDistance1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723848&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232235\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_maxDistance1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"92a54d5f-3097-48c9-afce-b0efe71b7bcc\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_maxDistance1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723848&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_maxDistance1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723848&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_maxDistance2.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_maxDistance2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723848&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_maxDistance2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723848&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232232\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_maxDistance2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"db77d3fe-95cc-40cb-8c43-a47b52236dae\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_maxDistance2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723848&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_maxDistance2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723848&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h4 id=\"PxrOcclusion-Falloff\">Falloff</h4><p>Falloff can be used to control the softness of the occlusion effect.</p><p>Without <strong>Max Distance</strong>, falloff is calculated as an exponential falloff. Values are scene dependent with larger values creating a softer look.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_falloff0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloff0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723503&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloff0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723503&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232220\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_falloff0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ef23b856-9b4e-4591-9d80-7d5db25b4b81\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloff0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723503&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloff0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723503&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_falloff1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloff1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloff1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232223\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_falloff1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c3d7ef94-27eb-4d02-8366-90f7d48d1718\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloff1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloff1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_falloff2.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloff2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloff2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232226\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_falloff2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"0c53878f-ef32-4de6-a756-fbe68c691f8e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloff2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloff2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723676&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>When combined with <strong>Max Distance</strong>, falloff is calculated as a normalized power function.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_falloffMaxDistance0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloffMaxDistance0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723502&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloffMaxDistance0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723502&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232214\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_falloffMaxDistance0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5d34e872-017f-45d3-b0a4-6bf163442f86\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloffMaxDistance0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723502&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloffMaxDistance0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723502&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_falloffMaxDistance1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloffMaxDistance1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723503&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloffMaxDistance1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723503&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232217\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_falloffMaxDistance1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"47264481-bf3f-43d3-99e0-6b7d2e45f33f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloffMaxDistance1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723503&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_falloffMaxDistance1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723503&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h4 id=\"PxrOcclusion-UseAlbedo\">Use Albedo</h4><p>When on, this setting applies the diffuse color to the resulting image. This may be a simple color or pattern attached to the material.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_useAlbedo1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_useAlbedo1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723294&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_useAlbedo1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723294&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232211\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_useAlbedo1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"7e3cf0bd-1196-4f49-984f-c3d6f96a693b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_useAlbedo1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723294&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_useAlbedo1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723294&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span><h4 id=\"PxrOcclusion-NumSamples\">Num Samples</h4><p>This option generates fixed samples at each shaded point. More samples may help resolve noise in fewer camera samples, but may reduce performance at higher numbers.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_numSamples0.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_numSamples0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_numSamples0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232205\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_numSamples0.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c7b1fd8e-b4f1-4fee-b36c-a9d2a2dc7580\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_numSamples0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_numSamples0.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" alt=\"PxrOcclusion_numSamples1.png\" width=\"384\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_numSamples1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542232193/PxrOcclusion_numSamples1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542232208\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrOcclusion_numSamples1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542232193\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"edd62a81-d684-431a-ae39-b6286f8e8aeb\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_numSamples1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542232193/PxrOcclusion_numSamples1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330723293&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
